== 感情生活 ==
廖碧兒曾與[[劉愷威|劉愷威]]及[[陳豪|陳豪]]拍拖，其後又與[[李澤楷|李澤楷]]表弟[[林忠豪|林忠豪]]傳出緋聞。直至2018年3月，被記者拍下與年約40歲的男友[[盧啟賢|盧啟賢]]（Calvin Lo）結伴遊芬蘭。及後廖碧兒直認兩人發展中，欣賞男方言行一致，亦透露他更曾跪地送驚喜<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://bka.mpweekly.com/interview/%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82123/20180317-105696 |title=【廖碧兒專訪】男友跪地送驚喜 「多年來沒人像他一樣」 |access-date=2018-03-29 |archive-date=2018-11-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181120170640/https://bka.mpweekly.com/interview/%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82123/20180317-105696 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。惟在同年7月底，拍拖不足半年的廖碧兒宣布分手，分手原因被指是男方本已有一名[[泰國人|泰籍]]女友但對感情狀況多番隱瞞，廖碧兒在這段關係中淪為第三者<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/entertainment/20180728/00282_001.html |title=廖碧兒難忍被瞞騙閃飛富二代 |date=2018-07-28 |work=東方日報 |accessdate=2018-07-28 |archive-date=2019-09-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190913203922/http://www.orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/entertainment/20180728/00282_001.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |url=https://bka.mpweekly.com/focus/20180727-124571 |title=與盧啟賢拍拖半年 廖碧兒宣布分手 |date=2018-07-28 |work=明報 |accessdate=2018-07-28 |archive-date=2018-07-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180729045934/https://bka.mpweekly.com/focus/20180727-124571 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |url=https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20180728/20462205 |title=前日傳秘嫁法酒莊富豪有蹺蹊 碧兒突宣佈「分」訊 甩富二代Calvin |date=2018-07-28 |work=蘋果日報 |accessdate=2018-07-28 |archive-date=2019-05-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190520173856/https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20180728/20462205 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

在2018年7月，傳出廖碧兒在2014年已秘嫁法國[[波爾多|波爾多]]酒莊富豪Charles Cazes，戀盧啟賢只是煙幕。<ref>{{Cite web|title=【再澄清冇結婚】廖碧兒宣佈同富二代盧啟賢分手|url=http://www.singtao.ca/toronto/2973396/2018-07-27/post-%e3%80%90%e5%86%8d%e6%be%84%e6%b8%85%e5%86%87%e7%b5%90%e5%a9%9a%e3%80%91%e5%bb%96%e7%a2%a7%e5%85%92%e5%ae%a3%e4%bd%88%e5%90%8c%e5%af%8c%e4%ba%8c%e4%bb%a3%e7%9b%a7%e5%95%9f%e8%b3%a2%e5%88%86%e6%89%8b/?variant=zh-hk|work=星島日報 加拿大 多倫多|date=2018-07-27|accessdate=2019-02-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190209123826/http://www.singtao.ca/toronto/2973396/2018-07-27/post-%e3%80%90%e5%86%8d%e6%be%84%e6%b8%85%e5%86%87%e7%b5%90%e5%a9%9a%e3%80%91%e5%bb%96%e7%a2%a7%e5%85%92%e5%ae%a3%e4%bd%88%e5%90%8c%e5%af%8c%e4%ba%8c%e4%bb%a3%e7%9b%a7%e5%95%9f%e8%b3%a2%e5%88%86%e6%89%8b/?variant=zh-hk|archive-date=2019-02-09|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=【短暫愛情】與富二代盧啟賢拍拖未夠半年 廖碧兒ig宣佈分手|url=https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180727/58492384|work=Apple Daily 蘋果日報|accessdate=2019-02-07|archive-date=2019-05-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190520190747/https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180727/58492384|dead-url=no}}</ref>秘婚新聞被揭發後，廖碧兒即時宣佈與盧啟賢分手。<ref>{{Cite web|title=【再澄清冇結婚】廖碧兒宣佈同富二代盧啟賢分手|url=http://hd.stheadline.com/life/ent/realtime/1276686/|work=頭條日報 Headline Daily|accessdate=2019-02-07|archive-date=2019-05-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190520052355/http://hd.stheadline.com/life/ent/realtime/1276686/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=澄清從沒秘婚 廖碧兒認與富二代盧啟賢分手|url=http://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/3315208/|work=www.bastillepost.com|accessdate=2019-02-07}}</ref>

